      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA FLAVOUR (6) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Roma Keeping (30.28) in a Restricted WIN. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Makes plenty of appeal. NON STOP WHISKEY (7) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.92 beating Black Raspberry. Has never missed the frame from three starts from this draw, including a win. Significant danger. MILCHICK (2) has been in super consistent form recently with two minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing sixth (26.01) at Q Lakeside. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Better than last start and can bounce back. WARM HUGS (1) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
